            "text": "<p>Built for sustained output and limited pocket space, road riders favor close-fitting layers that breathe well and pack small. As the weather warms, the system stays minimal and highly adjustable.</p><p></p><ul><li><strong>Hot:</strong> bib shorts + lightweight performance jersey</li><li><strong>Temperate:</strong> performance jersey with arm warmers or a packable vest</li><li><strong>Chilly mornings / descents:</strong> lightweight base layer + breathable thermal or grid jersey + packable shell</li></ul>",
