        "text_HHxrFc": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "subheading": "keeping it local",
            "title": "MADE IN USA",
            "heading_font_size": "heading-large",
            "text": "<p>We prioritize U.S. manufacturing because proximity brings accountability. Working closely with our sewing partners allows us to maintain quality, move quickly, and build real relationships with the people who make our products possible. </p><p>While great products are made all over the world, producing domestically aligns with how we want to operate, investing in skilled labor, strengthening the local economy, and supporting a more responsible production system. It’s not a tagline. It’s a commitment we continue to stand behind.</p>",
            "text_font_size": "body-small",
            "button_text": "",
            "button_url": "shopify://pages/1-for-the-planet",
