    "section_custom_content_FpQ6D7": {
      "type": "section-custom-content",
      "blocks": {
        "text_nWgT6r": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "subheading": "what's old is new again",
            "title": "RIGHT TO REPAIR",
            "heading_font_size": "heading-large",
            "text": "<p>Durability is one of the most effective sustainability strategies there is. We build our gear to last for years, and we stand behind it with a <strong>one-year warranty</strong> against manufacturer defects. Wear happens, and when it does, we believe in the right to repair.</p><p>Our repair program addresses common issues so products stay in use, not in landfills. Repairing almost always has a lower environmental impact than replacing. By backing what we make and supporting repairs, we reduce waste and honor the value of well-made clothing.</p>",
            "text_font_size": "body-small",
            "button_text": "start a repair",
            "button_url": "shopify://pages/1-for-the-planet",
            "button_type": "btn--primary",
